DocAttribute.Name: TheoryType
DocAttribute.Documentation: Specifies the analysis theory used to obtain the respective results.

DocAttribute.Name: IsLinear
DocAttribute.Documentation: This Boolean value allows to easily recognize if a linear analysis has been applied (allowing the superposition of analysis results), or vice versa.

DocAttribute.Name: ResultGroupFor
